api_list.name: Get Category
Get Currency
api_list.description:
**`code`**: This is the currency code.
**`name`**: This is the full name of the currency.
**`unicode_symbol`**: This is the Unicode symbol.

api_list.name: Get Languages
api_list.description:
**`title`**: This attribute specifies the language used.
**`subtitle`**: This attribute indicates the relevant region or country.
**`locale`**: This attribute combines the language code and the country code.

api_list.name: Auto-complete
api_list.description:
**`location_name`**:  This is the specific name of the location.
**`display_name`**:  This is the abbreviated name of the location displayed.
**`place_id`**:  This is a unique identifier used to reference the specific location.
**`country_code`**:  This is the country code for the location.
